Bulbapedia
:
Privacy policy
From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigation
Jump to search
Bulbagarden recognizes the importance of protecting the privacy of all information provided by users of Bulbagarden. We created the following policy guidelines with a fundamental respect for our users' right to privacy.
Bulbagarden ("us", "we", or "our") operates Bulbapedia (
https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net
), Bulbanews (
https://bulbanews.bulbagarden.net/
), the Bulbagarden Archives (
https://archives.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Main_Page
), the Bulbagarden Handbooks (
http://bulbahandbook.bulbagarden.net/
), the Bulbagarden forums (
http://forums.bulbagarden.net/index.php
) - collectively, the "Services". This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Services and the choices you have associated with that data.
We use your data to provide and improve the Service. By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
The policy below is effective as of September 13th, 2022.
